Indications in the context of respiratory conditions. 
 Sambucus nigra is indicated for fever and inflammation of the respiratory tract (
 WHO, 2002; 
 BRASIL, 2011). Other indications are to relieve cold and flu symptoms, to alleviate headaches, and as expectorant (
 EMA, 2018e; 
 Torabian et al., 2019).
